        "answer": "一点儿",
        "distractors": ["一些", "很多", "非常"],
        "english": "Can this piece of clothing be a little cheaper?"
      },
      {
        "sentence": "我肚子有___饿。",
        "answer": "一点儿",
        "distractors": ["很多", "非常", "太"],
        "english": "I'm a little hungry."
      },
      {
        "sentence": "请你说得快___。",
