    "level": 2,
    "title": "Desire with 想 (xiǎng)",
    "pattern": "Subject + 想 + Verb",
    "explanation": "想 means 'want to' or 'would like to' when followed by a verb. It expresses a desire or intention. It can also mean 'to miss (someone/something)' or 'to think'.",
