        "answer": "会",
        "distractors": ["想", "能", "可以"],
        "english": "She can play the piano."
      },
      {
        "sentence": "他___游泳吗？",
        "answer": "会",
        "distractors": ["想", "能", "是"],
        "english": "Can he swim?"
      },
